videos.description: David Nichols cues the Albany break as Campbell draws contact and finishes at the hoop.
videos.headline: Albany's Campbell finishes with contact for the three-point play

videos.description: Mike Rowley threads the pass to David Nichols for the easy basket.
videos.headline: Albany's Rowley finds Nichols on the Give & Go

videos.description: Dre Wills takes the feed from Cam Ward and floats it in.
videos.headline: Vermont's Wills shows the soft touch on the floater

videos.description: Dre Willis shows why he was voted the American East  Defensive Player of the Year with the huge block.
videos.headline: Vermont's Dre Wills with the big-time rejection

videos.description: Dre Wills blocks his second shot of the possession, forces Albany 24-second violation.
videos.headline: Vermont's Wills blocks the three-point attempt

videos.description: Trae Bell-Haynes runs the break and makes the layup.
videos.headline: Vermont's Bell-Haynes goes full-court, draws contact on the layup

videos.description: David Nichols recovers the loose ball and passes to Travis Charles who absorbs the contact and finishes in the lane. Albany's six point advantage is its largest lead of the game.
videos.headline: Albany takes its largest lead of game on Charles off-balance layup

videos.description: Anthony Lamb blocks leads to Albany break as Trae Bell-Haynes feeds to Kurt Steidl who hits the triple.
videos.headline: Defense leads to offense for Vermont, as Lamb block leads to Steidl triple

videos.description: Kurt Steidl hits the 3-point jumper to even the score, extend the run to 10-3 run.
videos.headline: Vermont's  Steidl hits the 3 to tie the game

videos.description: Trae Bell-Haynes drives the baseline, draws in the defense, and dishes to Payton Henson for the and-one.
videos.headline: Vermont's Bell-Haynes draws three defenders, finds Henson for the lead

videos.description: Albany's Joe Cremo drives the lane but Vermont's Peyton Henson meets him in the paint and takes the charge.
videos.headline: Vermont's Peyton Henson takes the charge

videos.description: Vermont wins the American East Championship over Albany 56-53.
videos.headline: Fans storm the court as Vermont clinches the 2016-17 American East Tournament Championship

videos.description: We join Mike Corey and Brooke Weisbrod as they talk to Vermont's Payton Henson and head coach John Becker
videos.headline: Postgame breakdown of Vermont's victory over Albany.
